          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections were determined in the delta (1232)",
                " excitation region for the reactions 3He(gamma,p)pn and",
                " 2H(gamma,p)n at several photon energies and proton",
                " emission angles. Inclusive proton spectra were",
                " measured with a magnetic spectrometer, using a",
                " quasimonochromatic e+ - annihilation photons. The",
                " 3He data can Be mainly accounted for by predictions",
                " assuming photon absorption  by a pair of nucleons,",
                " except in the high-momentum parts of the proton",
                " spectra. They clearly indicate the need for",
                " additional contributions, such as three-body",
                " absorption mechanism."
              ]
            }
          ],
